Please see the other .readme files and website [1] for detailed
documentation.

pitrtools is a Python + PostgreSQL application that assists in the
provisioning of Hot Standby, Warm Standby, Cold Standby, Streaming 
Replication clusters and multiple standbys (slaves). It supports 
all PostgreSQL versions from 8.2+ including 9.2.

Requirements:

 * Rsync
 * Python >= 2.6
 * SSH
 * PostgreSQL 8.2+

Website:

https://public.commandprompt.com/projects/pitrtools/wiki
